    "The digital divide also exacerbates social inequalities, limiting access to AI tools for underprivileged students [50].",
    "A more detailed discussion of these ethical issues and potential strategies for mitigation is provided in Sect. 5.2.",
    "Research gaps and opportunitiesMuch research has already taken place on the implications of AI in education and sustainability, but little on the overlap of the two at the higher education level.",
